        "filename": "util/net/http_transport_libcurl.cc",
        "patchSetId": 14
      },
      "lineNbr": 64,
      "author": {
        "id": 1172779
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-04-06T00:44:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I removed the CHECKs. The library is loaded and symbols resolved in Initialize() and if that fails HttpTransport::Create() returns nullptr. The symbols are resolved in Initialize() to avoid dealing with any cleanup from dealing with those failures in the middle of an upload and lazy resolution didn\u0027t seem useful.",
      "parentUuid": "1781a2df_6d64a692",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 63,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 64,
        "endChar": 41
      },
